{
  "stem": "27748.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then something kept gnawing at me that said, I must go back, I want to go back, I have to go back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that became stronger and stronger in me that I must go back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, I said maybe I can find out something more about the last days of my parents while they were there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe I can find out something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in reality, I didn't really know what was pulling me or pushing me or driving me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So eventually, I did go back for one day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was then still married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was divorced later, but I was still married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was really with the help of my wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I would not have had the courage to go back alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, in order to go back, I had to-- I wanted to make some arrangements to-- to contact some people there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't-- I remembered every Jewish person in the village, what they looked like, how nice they were, how crazy they were, where they sat in the synagogue, how they said their prayers, what work they did, how crazy they were in their personal lives.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I could mention stories about each person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I did not remember a single Christian, not a name, not a face, nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I wiped them out, despite the fact that we lived next to Christians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were not a separate ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the German system, you lived within the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I could not remember a single Christian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I asked my sister, my older sister, for names of people in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she remembered names, schoolmates she'd gone to school with, two women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I wrote to them beforehand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They wrote back, very warm, very loving, inviting us to come.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
